text: Ragni Hestad (born 5 September 1968) is a Norwegian beach volleyball player, born in Bergen. She competed in the women's tournament at the 1996 Summer Olympics in Atlanta, with team mate Merita Berntsen. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:People from Bergen Category:Norwegian beach volleyball players Category:Olympic beach volleyball players of Norway Category:Beach volleyball players at the 1996 Summer Olympics
